DescUsage: <<
TeX-Font Metric (*.tfm), psfonts.map are provided in the tarball. Put them 
in $HOME.
On terminal type the commands
------------------------------
cp /sw/share/doc/extex/homefile/.extex ~/.
extex
------------------------------
Sample usage:
-------------
\catcode`{=1
\catcode`}=2
\write3{Hello World}
